@node "SCENE" "This issues article...

                        the scene and our problems!
                        ŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊ

This is some kind of reply to rob/cls "...& our problems" txt in tequila9.


Sysops
ŊŊŊŊŊŊ
It's true that allmost everyone has a bbs running, there are diffrent
reasons, but many does it just to get the latest, and if one trader stops
uploading he get's deleted within a month.
It might hard to realise that your best friend in the scene is an asshole,
but try it and see what happens, if you lose your co-sys access, and when
you ask why, he say's you are a lamer since you don't upload anymore,
then you know he's an sysop-asshole. It's getting more every day because
lamers get's into the scene easier than ever and that's our problem.


Files
ŊŊŊŊŊ
Lame boards are also responsable for most of adds in .lha files, for some
days ago i down'ed a file on 79k, i removed all adds, the archive was
now about 10k. It's true, and i know it's extreme, but on allmost all .lha
files there is about 4k that are lame adds. When things like this is
happening i begin to wonder, what is the use of this lame adding on all
files, it would be enough with one add from each board, but the latest is
to "bomb" all files with as many adds as possible, the adds has very
strange names ie. "++ FUCK YOU ++". Why can't all of you out there add one
ascii with ie. "myboard.displayme" it's much better. And if it's get
striped, so what...


The Scene
ŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊ
What has happend to the scene, there is to many lame boards around, i see
often boards give you 2/3 times credits or a free cc to the weektop winner.
What is this, it's pure lameness, nothing else! More and more boards around
does this, why, because it's to many lamers in the scene! He get's a modem
and call's the local wannabe elite-board and...


Cards
ŊŊŊŊŊ
I'm now comming to the next problem that get's bigger and bigger every day!
Cards, yes, it's to easy to get cards today.

What's happening in the scene is that a lamer get's a modem, and calls the
local elite board and the sysop has bought a card list, and he gives a card
to this lamer that don't even know the toll free number to at&t, and there
is new lamers every day from all over the world that want's to be elites.
Where should we begin to do something, well you might say that i should get
the latest /X hacker or the latest fuck virus, but i don't think so, it
would ofcourse be nice to see the wannabe board get formated and be offline,
but it wouldn't last long, after some days it would be back online and then
the hell starts all over, it has to be another way of fixing this problem.


Solution
ŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊ
That's to get rid of all card sellers, think about it, when blueboxing
was hot, it didn't coast anything, and the tones lasted forever.
With cards it's not that easy, because the cards don't last long and they
isn't free either. And there have become a alot of card sellers out there
that sell a card twice, when the buyers say it died to fast, the seller
blames it on at&t, but the buyers don't know it was sold twice and that's
the real reason why they died so fast, if at&t see the same card on two
diffrent calls they kill it. This has happend alot in the last period,
at&t has now set a limit on about 50$, if they reach 50 within a day they
kill it. And the quality get's worse and worse, and that's all those card
sellers who have sold cards to lamers that are the main reason this happens.

The real scene was about friendship, but where is that gone ... now it's
all about money, sad, but true.


Boards
ŊŊŊŊŊŊ
About lame boards, i'm not going to give you any name, but it has been
online for a long time at the same phone number, but the strange is that
the sysop and the board has changed names atleast 6-7 times, he claims
often he has had a crash or lost the user.data, but when logging with
normal access it's the same messages and old people that still are there,
but he wrote that he had lost his user.data! And why, well i don't know, if
he wanted to get rid of some lamers then he could have changed number a
long time a go, but no, instead he changed his name and board name and this
is happening frequently, i'm sick and tierd of boards that does such lame
things, what's the use, could it be that the sysop is extremely lame ...


Dists
ŊŊŊŊŊ
Groups that let pay dist's join their group is fucking lame, nothing else.
It's only lamers who pay so that they can be supported by a group trader,
this shows that some groups exists for money, money and more money ...
If there are some real groups with a little bit of respect left, stop
this now. If a board must pay to get support what's the point of having
that board online ... become a trader instead!


               Let's make friends - not war's in the scene!

